fer—A position as housekeeper at your employers' mansion! Along with a significant pay raise, you will also be given free room and board! <br><br>However, you'll be spending your time serving the owners of the mansion, who happen to be three unusually captivating sisters...<br><br>Prepare for a summer full of blush-worthy, heart-pounding escapades as you tend to the three sisters and your dependable supervisor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458860/extras/9220888ca5ee6fa5295e08566bc0bb41.poster.avif?t=1772721391\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458860/extras/9220888ca5ee6fa5295e08566bc0bb41.webm?t=1772721391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458860/extras/9220888ca5ee6fa5295e08566bc0bb41.mp4?t=1772721391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458860/extras/89f1df88a44c79b73db565694d858d6b.poster.avif?t=1772721391\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458860/extras/89f1df88a44c79b73db565694d858d6b.webm?t=1772721391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458860/extras/89f1df88a44c79b73db565694d858d6b.mp4?t=1772721391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2>Manage your time at the mansion as you venture through the lighthearted slice-of-life story.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Each character has their own fully-developed story<br></li><li> Japanese voice acting for the main female characters<br></li><li> An exciting array of events and CGs for you to discove